<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<sample sampleID="LBh9_00115" version="1.0" type="fixedLength">
<article articleID="LBh9_00115_F001">
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「なんだ…透<sampling type="start" />緒呼様」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　黒髪に、紫の瞳。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　そんな組み合わせを持つ人物は、この王宮にたった一人だ。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi"><sentence>　「どうか…なさったんですか？</sentence>
<sentence>　そんな格好で、こんな時間に？」</sentence>
</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　うすものの夜着一枚で、ふらふら、ふらふらと。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「もしかして…お酔いになってらっしゃるんですか？」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　〈くすくすくすっ〉</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　彼女は笑った。</sentence>
<sentence>あきらかに、異常な発音で。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「透緒呼・様？」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　いぶかって、侍女が首を<ruby rubyText="かし">傾</ruby>げる。</sentence>
<sentence>暗くて、その表情までは、くみとれない。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　〈くすくす〉</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　彼女は髪をかきあげて、笑った。</sentence>
<sentence>あざやかな紫の瞳が、侍女に強い印象をのこす。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　〈くす〉</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　ぺたり、ぱたり。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　ぎごちなく、彼女は踏み出した。</sentence>
<sentence type="quasi">そして、</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　〈くすくすくすくすくすくす、く…けけけけけけけけけけけけけ―ぼっ！〉</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「ッ！！」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　音を立てて、かき消える。</sentence>
<sentence>存在すらなかったように。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「…」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　ずるっ。</sentence>
<sentence>侍女は腰を抜かして、くず折れた。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「いまの―」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　透緒呼様じゃ・ない。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「じゃあ」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　『〈ヨウ・シ〉のユウレイ…』</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　がくがくと、いまさらながら、膝がふるえた。</sentence>
<sentence>腰から下の感覚が、にぶく<ruby rubyText="う">失</ruby>せてゆく。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　おそろしさに涙をにじませ、侍女は廊下を腕の力で移動しはじめた。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　やっとの思いで明かりの<ruby rubyText="つ">点</ruby>いている部屋まで<ruby rubyText="たど">辿</ruby>り着き、侍女はわずかな透き間から手を入れ、扉を開け放った。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「あれ、どうしたの？」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　なじみの若い官僚が声をかける。</sentence>
<sentence>彼女が恐ろしい目にあったなど、これっぽちも知らない彼は明るい笑顔だった。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　ほッ。</sentence>
<sentence>侍女から力が抜ける。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「あ、おいっ！」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　官僚が駆け寄る足音を耳に、彼女は意識を手放した。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　その体験が噂になるのは、三日後。</sentence>
<sentence>彼女の意識が回復してからのことである。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<titleBlock>
<title>
<sentence type="quasi">第三章　霧の<ruby rubyText="きば">牙</ruby></sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</title>
</titleBlock>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　ひそひそと王宮にささやきが流れる。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　（このあいだ）</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　（このあいだのこと、聞いた？）</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　（〈<ruby rubyText="ヨウ">陽</ruby><ruby rubyText="シ">使</ruby>〉）</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　（〈陽使人形〉のこと）</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　（黒髪に紫の瞳の、〈陽使〉の幽霊のこと）</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　さざなみのように<ruby rubyText="ひそ">密</ruby>やかな、けれどたしかな〈噂〉。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　（<ruby rubyText="ト">透</ruby><ruby rubyText="オ">緒</ruby><ruby rubyText="コ">呼</ruby>様に）</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　（<ruby rubyText="カイ">界</ruby><ruby rubyText="ザ">座</ruby>第二公女・透緒呼様に）</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　（〈銀聖色〉のない透緒呼様に）</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　（そっくり）</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　（そっくりだったんですってよ…）</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　王宮を騒がせた者たちの共通点に、人々は気付いてしまった。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　（いままでのも）</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　（今までの幽霊も）</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　（みんな）</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　（みんな紫の瞳で）</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　（まあ！）</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　（じゃあ！）</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　（透緒呼様は―？）</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　（ヨウ…）</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　ばんっ！</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　通路館のすみにたまって、こそこそと話をしていた<ruby rubyText="じ">侍</ruby><ruby rubyText="じょ">女</ruby>たちの会話を、するどい音がやぶった。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「やめろよそんな話」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　おさえた声に、ぎくッ、彼女らは振り向いた。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「アラ、シャ殿…」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　ガラスの壁を叩いたままの格好で、<ruby rubyText="ア">亜</ruby><ruby rubyText="ラ">羅</ruby><ruby rubyText="シャ">写</ruby>が彼女らをにらみつけている。</sentence>
<sentence>怒りで、エセラがかがやきはじめていた。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「し、失礼しました」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　ばたばたと侍女たちが散ってゆく。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「―」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　亜羅写はいまいましそうにそれを見送り、ようやく壁から手をはなした。</sentence>
<sentence>頭を一振りして、後宮の方へ歩きだす。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　マッタク。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　苦い言葉がわいた。</sentence>
<sentence>当たり所のないむしゃくしゃが、たまってくる。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　かつてのように、人々に、ふたたび透緒呼への不信が持ち上がりはじめていた。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　恐怖の一致。</sentence>
<sentence>〈銀聖色〉を持たない人間と、おなじ<sampling type="end" />組み合わせを持つ〈陽使〉の<ruby rubyText="はい">徘</ruby><ruby rubyText="かい">徊</ruby>―。</sentence>
</paragraph>
</article>
</sample>
